MacOS Build Instructions
========================

Setup
-----

build-tree
	alsp_src
	mwbuild
	tcltk_interface
	alsdev

Installed Tcl/Tk.

Build
-----

Make alspro_b in the mwbuild directory and move it to the alsdev folder.

In alsdev, setup an alsdir with the folders "builtins" and "library".

Copy the file tcltk.pro into the alsdev folder. Remove consult of "tclintf".

Run alspro_b and consult "mac_make.pro" to build all necessary obp files.

Open mac_alsdev.mcp.

Make "PPC Build" to create "ALS Prolog PPC".

Runtime Setup
-------------

Here is the minimal runtime setup.  Optional additions are alsdir:library, examples, etc.

ALS Prolog PPC
